<span id="freeTextContainer8814155624505661334">This is horrific and very honest. Another must for anybody who wants to spend time in the region and wants to understand how it can all go wrong very quickly. It’s incredible how people still tend to blame the colonial past for today’s problems. It’s time that we started to take responsibility for our own actions now.</span>

          </span>
